OL,3,CNHS staff 'made heartless criticisms
OL,4,Cabout families in maternity review'
OL,6,FThe review began three years ago after
OL,7,Fallegations of harm to babies and
OL,8,Fmothers, and now involves nearly 2,500
OL,9,Ffamilies.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the trust's annual public
OL,12,Fmeeting on Wednesday, the trust's
OL,13,Fchief executive Anthony May said the
OL,14,Fcomments allegedly made about the
OL,15,Ffamilies are "shocking".
