OL,3,CNHS staff 'made heartless criticisms
OL,4,Cabout families in maternity review'
OL,6,FDuring the meeting, Mr May said: "Some
OL,7,Ffamilies very recently have fed back
OL,8,Fto me shocking examples of being
OL,9,Fstigmatised or gaslit ` criticised for
OL,10,Feither being part of the independent
OL,11,Freview or for campaigning for better
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,F"Families have heard that they are
OL,15,Fcriticised for being in the review,
OL,16,Fand that they are in the review on the
OL,17,Fbasis that they are seeking
OL,18,Fcompensation.
OL,26,@nD@bOUvD@AOU
