OL,3,CNHS staff 'made heartless criticisms
OL,4,Cabout families in maternity review'
OL,6,F"The families tell me that there are
OL,7,Finstances where they feel they have
OL,8,Freason to believe they can trace that
OL,9,Fback to colleagues that work in NUH."
OL,11,FDr Jack and Sarah Hawkins, who both
OL,12,Fused to work for the trust until their
OL,13,Fdaughter Harriet was stillborn in
OL,14,F2016, have been campaigning to expose
OL,15,Ffailures at NUH ever since.
OL,17,FThey described the comments as
OL,18,F"horrific" and "unfathomably
OL,19,Fheartless".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]zD@AOUzD@JO]zD@POU{D@JO]
