OL,3,CNHS staff 'made heartless criticisms
OL,4,Cabout families in maternity review'
OL,6,FDr Hawkins said: "We have been called
OL,7,F'compo seekers'. There has been a
OL,8,Fcomment made that people are in this
OL,9,Fgroup because they have been groomed
OL,10,Fby Sarah and I and other people who
OL,11,Fhave been around for a long time, and
OL,12,Fthat has come out of NUH.
OL,14,F"We want change. We don't have any
OL,15,Fother reason to be in this fight.
OL,26,@nD@ROUvD@AOU
