OL,3,CNHS staff 'made heartless criticisms
OL,4,Cabout families in maternity review'
OL,6,F"The first thing to allow you to
OL,7,Fchange is to recognise that you need
OL,8,Fto change. And if your attitude is
OL,9,Fthat you don't and that we are, in
OL,10,Ffact, scamming the system in some way,
OL,11,Fthen it's so disheartening.
OL,13,F"We're not doing this for any reason
OL,14,Fother than babies are dying and being
OL,15,Fharmed and mums are dying and being
OL,16,Fharmed and families are being ripped
OL,17,Fapart.
OL,19,F"To reduce that down to... 'they're
OL,20,Fseeking compensation' is unfathomably
OL,21,Fheartless."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@KO]
