OL,6,FMrs Hawkins said: "Life couldn't get
OL,7,Fany worse... and then they said this
OL,8,Fabout us, and we just feel like these
OL,9,Fcomplete utter monsters, shouldn't be
OL,10,Fworking in a caring profession."
OL,12,FDr and Mrs Hawkins said they
OL,13,F"absolutely" think there should be
OL,14,Fdisciplinary action against staff who
OL,15,Fmade the comments.
