OL,6,FDr Hawkins said: "We're not going to
OL,7,Fbe called 'compo seekers'. We're not
OL,8,Fgoing to be shamed after what happened
OL,9,Fto us, it is their responsibility to
OL,10,Ftake account for what they did and
OL,11,Fstart changing."
OL,13,FMr May said he wrote an email to each
OL,14,Fstaff member at the trust to explain
OL,15,Fthat the comments are "not acceptable".
