OL,6,F"The families I've met are some of the
OL,7,Fmost courageous people I've ever come
OL,8,Facross, who have not only suffered
OL,9,Flifelong trauma, but they're happy to
OL,10,Ftell their experiences over and over
OL,11,Fagain to try and improve (services).
OL,13,F"The vast majority of people who work
OL,14,Fin the trust would never, ever, dream
OL,15,Fof doing that... but if they do, then
OL,16,Fthere are processes that we can use to
OL,17,Fdeal with that."
